Power BI Template Requirements
==============================

Place your Power BI template file here as: model.pbit

The template must:
1. Use a Text parameter named "BaseFolder"
2. Reference tables using relative paths:
   - (BaseFolder)\star\dim_dataset.csv
   - (BaseFolder)\star\dim_column.csv
   - (BaseFolder)\star\fact_profile_runs.csv
   - (BaseFolder)\star\fact_quality_metrics.csv
   - (BaseFolder)\time\dim_time.csv

3. Mark dim_time as a Date Table
4. Set up relationships as defined in relationships.json

To create the template:
1. Open Power BI Desktop
2. Create parameter: BaseFolder (Text) = "./dist"
3. Import CSVs using the parameter in paths
4. Set up relationships
5. Mark dim_time as date table
6. Save as template (.pbit)
